snippet.textDisplay: Tom, so glad u r washing ur car yourself and listening! You do need to get yourself a proper snow foam cannon, plenty of them come with karcher adapters. You also need to get some chemical guys honeydew snow foam. You will then notice how much better shaving cream like snow foam you get from your snow foam cannon. The karcher soap n snow cannon is a watery joke. The Purpose for having thick snow foam on the car is to prevent you from installing scratches and swirls in the paint when you wash with your wash mitt. The very thick snow foam provides much needed lubrication prior to making contact with the paint with your wash mit. You also need a dedicated Iron remover product to properly spray and wash your wheels to remove brake dust. Good luck man! If you haven’t already I’d highly suggest having the merc fully ceramic coated. You will then see how much easier it is to maintain your car let alone wash it !

You also need a dedicated Iron remover product to properly spray and wash your wheels to remove brake dust. Good luck man! If you haven’t already I’d highly suggest having the merc fully ceramic coated. You will then see how much easier it is to maintain your car let alone wash it !
